Thanks.

Subject: Metrics Confirmation
Hi [Name],
Can you confirm if we are including cancelled orders in this metric?
Regards.

Subject: Priority Check
Hi [Name],
Should I prioritize this over the weekly report?
Thanks.

Subject: Request for Reference
Hi Team,
Do we have a previous version of this report for reference?
Regards.

